name: WestJet "Magic Plane" 737-8CT [C-GWSZ] Taxi and Takeoff from Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Despite this livery being around for almost three years now, I don't think I've ever gotten a video of it that I actually liked. Glad I fixed that! Here we have C-GWSZ, WestJet's amazing "Magic Plane" taxiing and taking off from Calgary Airport on runway 17L a couple weeks ago, off to Hamilton. ATC is included, hope you enjoy this awesome livery!

Thanks for watching!

-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

Airline: WestJet (WJA/WS)
Aircraft: Boeing 737-800 (B738)
Aircraft Name: "Sorcerer Mickey"

Runway used: 17L shortened
